# Coverage data: this repo ships only the demo companies. Companies you research
# are ignored by default, so your private coverage never lands in a public repo.
# The allowlist below is regenerated from DEMO_IDS (site/build.mjs) by
# alfred-private's sync-to-public workflow — don't hand-edit it here.
data-dumps/*
!data-dumps/.gitkeep
!data-dumps/NTSK
!data-dumps/CRWV
!data-dumps/AVGO
!data-dumps/APP
!data-dumps/FIG
!data-dumps/databricks
